íQatelghii tapgham qukaani mallungluni ayveghmeng neghumaluku sunanguq taana amaa. Kaalluni amaam qatelghii pimakanga, “Whangallu neqaghlanga. Igatapigtunga.” “Legan neghi. Uglaghllagtuq. Whanga-ngingaghma naangnnaanghitaqa.” Llaaghanwha amaallu neghumalghii. Iwemgaqun kepsughlutek neghlutek tapgham kelutanganilngughmun uusneghwaaghmun mayuumalghiik. Qaygeghsamek qatelghiim amaa pimakanga, “Whani yeqay meghnaaliltung. Wiin qavaaltung.” Llaaghanwha amaa aanghumalghii.
îTawani uusneghwaaghem qaayngani ingaghquusimalghiik. Qatelghii qavaghpenani teghhumaamalghii. Amaa qavaghyan whaa tungunghaqasan qatelghii nekevluni tamaani qemgughtimalghii ayveghem kuyapegaaneng. Qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii nuuvulluki amaam paapgakun qilleghsi-makangi.
