“Seghleghhalekkaannaqaatnga anguyaget. Tuqunnaqaatnga. Awitwuwaqlu papemkun kiitegtaatnga. Sangami paapka aqnighaqa?” Amaa iwemgaqun qevuulluni qimakaq tuqunnayukangatni. Qimaguqestaghngaaghmi kinguminilnguq kavlek almesiqngiinaghyagu saama pekapigsami amaa sumeghtaghaamalghii, “Qaywaam tuqulanga.” Aghuliighutkelluku uteghmun qiivyalghiimi sughumeng esghaanneghituq. Katam taawa paapgakun qilleghlluteng qafsinat ayveghem kuyapegii. Amaa pimalghii, “Uguminaghnaghhalek qatelghiipenaaq pekaghtepigtaanga. Kergam taawa esghaqaghtekumken unguvallequten.”
íQatelghiim kiiwek kaallukek akimun ayuqelghiik maligsimakek iwemgam esnamun. Tawani esnami tepameng neghemsuglimi taglaamalghii esnam kelutanganun. Pengughaghhaghmun kaalluni tawani qavaghnaqsami iyegni nusugraghlukek saaghwmikun llilukek qavaamalghii. Taagken amaam ugumiyagulluku qatelghii tamaghhaani ivaghtaayaqenni. Qenwatlu naalkeqaghsimakanga. Qatelghii qavaghaqeftuq enngaatall umuluku naqam saaghwani iyek. Amaamtaghsaghpenaan iiskekqatelghiimtutmaghtaalukek qageghqughlukek unisimakanga. Kingunganeng amaam qatelghiim iwemgaqun qavagni nusuglukek taghtughyami iyegni tugunaqsaqegni aviituk. Katamnaalkumakekqageghqughlleraaghinaak. Qatelghii ayaaluni paneghluni tuqumalghii.
